{"title":"“人权”颂","authors":["天马　江帆"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":1,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“人权”颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马诗　江帆画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年12月10日至17日，是肯尼迪宣布的所谓“人权周”。而在12日至16日期间，美国佐治亚州小城沃尔巴尼的监狱，却顿然有人满之患，近八百名反对种族歧视的黑人、白人、妇女和儿童被关进这里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总统讲人权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口水飞上天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心平脸不热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修养不一般！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"权属什么人？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人有什么权？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魔怪威风抖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民坐牢监！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强盗坐公堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好人受审判；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老爷肥胖胖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百姓骨熬干！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好个“金元国”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事情颠倒颠！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何必施脂粉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尊容太难看！（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}